%h1.page-header New Visualization

.form.vis-form{role: 'form'}
  = form_for @visualization, remote: true, format: :json do |f|
    = render 'shared/error_messages'
    = render 'shared/success_messages'

    .col-md-9.col-sm-12

      #vis-new

      .row
        .col-xs-12
          %ol
            %li
              Scalable prosperity voice vulnerable citizens, assistance; non-partisan socio-economic divide. Respect nonprofit achieve; amplify inspiration; maintain.  Inclusive metrics combat HIV/AIDS innovate. Public service legal aid strengthen democracy; John Lennon fellows tackling diversity foundation institutions.
            %li
              Organization volunteer community health workers communities impact inspire social change partnership natural resources board of directors. Legitimize eradicate civil society; necessities fundraise social innovation lasting change citizens of change revitalize. Sustainable climate change Bill and Melinda Gates accelerate progress Kickstarter. Open source readiness cross-agency.
            %li
              Jane Jacobs working families Bono complexity protect. Partner; growth participatory monitoring billionaire philanthropy solution. Medicine forward-thinking; time of extraordinary change Rockefeller UNICEF. International emergency response, rights-based approach, tackle change, life-expectancy, economic independence employment rural development.

    .col-md-3.col-sm-12

      .form-group
        = f.label      :title
        = f.text_field :title, class: 'form-control'
      .form-group
        = f.label      :year, 'Year(s)'
        = f.text_field :year,  class: 'form-control'
      .form-group
        = f.label      :abstract
        = f.text_area  :abstract, class: 'form-control'
      .form-group
        = f.label :issue_area_ids, 'Topics'
        %p.small Hold down Control (PC) or Command (Mac) to select multiple topics.
        = f.collection_select :issue_area_ids, IssueArea.all, :id, :title, {}, {multiple: true, class: 'form-control'}
      .form-group
        = f.label :data_source_ids, 'Data Sources'
        %p.small Hold down Control (PC) or Command (Mac) to select multiple data sources.
        = f.collection_select :data_source_ids, DataSource.all, :id, :title, {}, {multiple: true, class: 'form-control'}
      .form-group
        = f.label  :institution_id
        %br
        = f.collection_select(:institution_id, Institution.all, :id, :short_name, selected: @institution.id)
      .form-group
        = f.label  :permission, 'Public or Private?'
        %p.small
          Public visualizations are displayed in the gallery, and can be viewed and shared.
        = select_tag(:permission, options_for_select([['Public','public'],['Private','private']], 'public'))

      = f.hidden_field :sessionstate

      = f.submit 'Save', class: 'btn btn-large btn-success'

:javascript

$(document).on('ready', function () {
  DC.embedWeave($('#vis-new'));  
});
